{"tid":1514804,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"博爾頓：中国盜取美國F-35戰機技術","createTime":"2019-08-29T01:47:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T08:58:04.000Z","uid":184679,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"89ce81edc320ee6fdd793b3f177a3efde3443fb5","tid":1514804,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T01:47:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5d671ddb0062511817a9990e.jpg/JVMffiuZ5u0i9Miu2yb_sHO9GIw4MSkk3GZgt9xmYLc?v=w1600r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5d671ddb0062511817a9990e.jpg%2FJVMffiuZ5u0i9Miu2yb_sHO9GIw4MSkk3GZgt9xmYLc%3Fv%3Dw1600r16_9&h=650542f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國國家安全顧問博爾頓8月28日訪問烏克蘭首都基輔，在記者會期間表示，中國解放軍第五代戰機，與美國F-35戰機很像，是中國盜取回來。<br />\n<br />\n博爾頓（John Bolton）未有指出中國哪一架戰機盜取了美國F-35技術，中國第五代戰機有殲-20和仍在研發中的FC-31，但殲-20不論在型態上和構造上與F-35相差甚遠。<br />\n<br />\n博爾頓表示烏克蘭需提防中國的債務外交，並對中國的不公平貿易與危害國家安全的威脅表示擔憂，提醒烏克蘭與中國合作可能會被竊取知識產權。<br />\n<br />\n中國正計劃收購烏克蘭飛機引擎公司Motor Sich，美國《華爾街日報》報道指博爾頓正試圖阻止收購計劃。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/369152/%E5%8D%9A%E7%88%BE%E9%A0%93-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%9B%9C%E5%8F%96%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8Bf-35%E6%88%B0%E6%A9%9F%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93</code></pre>"},{"pid":"0b0681027b42d406b2dbb88660946749a6cbe9d4","tid":1514804,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T01:54:17.000Z","msg":"FC-31"},{"pid":"0750f8136cb497027cd1634529962a2602f1567d","tid":1514804,"uid":62811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:00:18.000Z","msg":"呢道偷啲嗰道砌啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"058f053599d0f204365b7d0ad4f71ee6b6f794f7","tid":1514804,"uid":116630,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:41:07.000Z","msg":"軍事科技呢d 野，邊有得講，真係比人偷到只能講自己做得不夠好。 不過，中國係真係偷到定得個樣就不知啦。"},{"pid":"1dce8f1a9338e457e1c1911945138e09fce430a5","tid":1514804,"uid":135408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:46:39.000Z","msg":"FC鬥....."},{"pid":"5b01a6d1c77ea518a9b5ca6bc9e9d3a6ceb7d71f","tid":1514804,"uid":39365,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:51:36.000Z","msg":"F35搞左超過十年, 經歷左黑鬼左膠年代, 俾共碟潛左入去偷野唔出奇"},{"pid":"5d2fc1dcb1e19ae6ab70628e7013006f67d55dfa","tid":1514804,"uid":99962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:53:04.000Z","msg":"F35用黎賣既姐<br />\n<br />\n主力係外星武器F22"},{"pid":"8cebd9fe36369af7dcf6e054e082f6af512e87dd","tid":1514804,"uid":244034,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d2fc1dcb1e19ae6ab70628e7013006f67d55dfa","tid":1514804,"uid":99962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:53:04.000Z","msg":"F35用黎賣既姐<br />\n<br />\n主力係外星武器F22"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:54:22.000Z","msg":"重開生產線既話應該仲利害"},{"pid":"f47f253357104005de4f0fdddd4f5cd1e2fe41b4","tid":1514804,"uid":235025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:56:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a56616bee89359c040b4b150d6cd9a812a1c2931","tid":1514804,"uid":268692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8cebd9fe36369af7dcf6e054e082f6af512e87dd","tid":1514804,"uid":244034,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d2fc1dcb1e19ae6ab70628e7013006f67d55dfa","tid":1514804,"uid":99962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:53:04.000Z","msg":"F35用黎賣既姐<br />\n<br />\n主力係外星武器F22"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:54:22.000Z","msg":"重開生產線既話應該仲利害"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:57:17.000Z","msg":"不過生產成本好撚高呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd56dc0cc38b0484d68356a871390fd18e94f0f9","tid":1514804,"uid":199235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T03:15:48.000Z","msg":"偷完都做唔到嫁啦.咪又係得個殼..<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces